value.0: This bit of foliage may have something concealed underneath...

Value.value: The curious eyes of some hiding animals observe you from close by. The deer seem a mite skittish, but nothing else is amiss.
The sounds of Brost fall away to complete serenity. You hear only the gentle conversation of the birds.
Only a few paces from the village, you could be in another world. A gentle green light dapples the trees in the clearing, and a deep calm settles over you in this place.
